# Train-hop credentials.
#
# Copy this file's contents to  ~/.mozbuild/trainhop.env  and fill in the values.
# (That path needs nothing but a local Firefox; it lives outside every repo so
#  the credentials are never committed.)
#
# Real environment variables override anything set here.

# Required: Bugzilla API key
#   bugzilla.mozilla.org -> your name -> Preferences -> API Keys -> Generate
BUGZILLA_API_KEY=

# That's the only key you need. Jira and Confluence are handled by the
# Atlassian MCP plugin (sign-in via OAuth, no token) — see references/credentials.md.
